Package: monographaR
Version: 1.01
Date: 2015-11-07
Title: Taxonomic Monographs Tools
Author: Marcelo Reginato
Maintainer: Marcelo Reginato <reginatobio@yahoo.com.br>
Depends: R (>= 3.0.0), maptools
Suggests: knitr
